  "body": "We run `solidity-coverage` to produce contract code coverage metrics. We should check these against thresholds for branch coverage to ensure we don't fall below the current state of `experimental` branch (`experimental` will soon be merged to `develop` but at the time of writing it's the branch you should be targeting). \r\nFor this threshold check, it's recommended to use `istanbul check-coverage` although we're open to alternative suggestions.  ",
